Episodes.Title: Nega-Timmy
Episodes.Plot: Timmy wishes to do the opposite of what his parents tell him to, and when they say be good, he turns evil.

Episodes.Title: Love at First Height
Episodes.Plot: Timmy becomes 16 to ride a rollercoaster and Vicky accidentally falls in love with him and everybody want's to be with Timmy believing that he's a Norwegian super model.

Episodes.Title: Truth or Cosmoquences
Episodes.Plot: Wanda and Timmy agree to help Cosmo impress people at his high school reunion by pretending he is rich and married to Britney Britney and that they are his secretary and his butler. It works perfectly, until Wandissimo shows up and decides to put the moves on Cosmo's ""secretary"" - - Wanda!!!

Episodes.Title: Beach Bummed
Episodes.Plot: Tired of having sand kicked in his face by Frances, Timmy wishes he was the strongest guy on the beach. But when a whale washes up on shore Timmy grows into a super-sized-hulking-human who quickly becomes the main target of a dangerously armed and heavily funded Seaweed Monster Response Team.

Episodes.Title: Just Desserts
Episodes.Plot: Timmy wishes every meal was dessert, but his wish makes the entire town fat.

Episodes.Title: You Doo!
Episodes.Plot: Timmy wishes for a You-Doo doll of Francis for revenge. Later on, Timmy gets You-Doo dolls of mostly every main character on the show. Tootie gets the You-Doo of Timmy, and the trouble starts!

Episodes.Title: Catman Meets the Crimson Chin
Episodes.Plot: Catman fights Crimson Chin Villains in an attempt to find acceptance

Episodes.Title: Back To Norm
Episodes.Plot: Mr. Crocker receives the magic lava lamp as a present and tries to capture Timmy's fairies in a Roadrunner-like manner

Episodes.Title: The Masked Magician
Episodes.Plot: Timmy becomes a super hero called "" The Masked Magician!"" Mr. Bickles gets mad at Timmy and becomes his arch-enemy
Episodes.Director: Ken Bruce, Juli Hashiguchi, Butch Hartman
